Enums within modules are working fine, but not within classes. 
```
class top;
typedef enum 
{
X,
Y
} xy;
endclass
```
The example above results in `error: invalid class item.` 

Icarus Verilog version 10.2 (stable) (v10_2), used with the following command: `iverilog -o class_example class_example.sv -g2012`

